title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 §§ 2600-6.3 - Complaint procedures
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 §§ 2600-6.3 - Complaint procedures

State Regulations

The department may establish and make publicly available by
instructions or other guidance procedures for filing complaints regarding tax
return preparers. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20
§§
2600-6.3

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
